Here is my guide to show how I got this work.

After you have loaded this torrent and installed the photoshop (don't log in at any adobe account) open the torrent Adobe CS5 folder-> CRACK. C:\Program Files\Adobe\Adobe Photoshop CS5 (64 Bit)\

If the C: disk don't work go to START MENU->COMPUTER and check out your disk letter and replace the C: for that.
